{"tid":1378624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[情緒問題] 今日好嬲，好灰，想放棄既，全部入黎！","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:17:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T06:35:37.000Z","uid":231905,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9b17626c9a6e28b3874851bf7cc720c76a74f3e8","tid":1378624,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:17:46.000Z","msg":"相信有朋友會有以上心情<br />\n我身邊有朋友情緒都好波動，時刻mon住連登，茶飯不思咁既樣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但咁樣點行落去！？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呼籲朋友如果覺得自己情緒唔好，<span style=\"color: red;\">一定要搵時間抽離下</span><br />\n發生事時要關心，相對平靜時都要把握機會休息，both生心理。<br />\n<br />\n打機時打機，睇戲就睇戲，拍拖就拍拖。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">處理好自己心智，先可以繼續走下去。</span><br />\n<br />\n(我自己係發夢派，發夢時發夢，完左一定係返去休息，重要資訊一定會睇，睇完就專心打機，睇戲，咩都好，穩定心態，唔可以比自己攰，所以我次次發夢都意志堅定。)"},{"pid":"af395f62ae18fee2c317d6cdfa0bcad6cbc2395a","tid":1378624,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:21:19.000Z","msg":"推少少算"},{"pid":"1fe842c9cc7bd997f0b75523d573402ae4ab66f7","tid":1378624,"uid":265019,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:21:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kDRaNgU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkDRaNgU.png&h=725f5888&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TOraNgV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTOraNgV.png&h=fe6acb72&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OjtwwJA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOjtwwJA.png&h=41e96b49&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fie37gV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffie37gV.png&h=f5471187&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6um2DoB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6um2DoB.png&h=6524cf57&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wJchsgW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"ht